		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Man I'm so glad about it. I finally own the real thing. And I've done two absolutely incredible things :
<br />- I beat turbo tunnel racing without loosing any lives on the very first try (tough I lose a life fighting rats before the racing part)
<br />- I kicked the 3rd bomb in Rat Race level. I got defeated by the boss tough, but I don't care I'm still SO proud !
<br />
<br />Honnestly it makes me so happy. So few people can state this. I still have to skip the Inferno using the warp tough, but I hope I'll be able to beat it too one day.

		

