	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" /><div class="quotetitle">Bregalad wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">The problem with inferno is those dumbs rockets. Kill me all the time, if anyone have a trick to avoid them please tell it.</div>
<br />
<br />The rockets that fire up from the bottom don't hit you if you stick to the bottom of the screen.  I usually just chill out in the lower-left corner of the screen.  You still have to dodge the rockets that come from the top though.
<br />
<br />Just don't go for the 1-up at the end of the rocket portion -- it's so not worth the risk.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
